{"tid":969665,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民疑「翻牆」太多　遭公安罰1千人仔","createTime":"2019-01-05T08:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T09:54:05.000Z","uid":66271,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"da2d69adcc3d7459413e537c6120adea9f70f364","tid":969665,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190105/photo/bkn-20190105141443415-0105_00952_001_01p.jpg?20190105162434\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190105141443415-0105_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20190105162434&h=0ac91f45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地嚴控網絡活動，不少市民為了接觸境外網站如Google、Facebook、YouTube等，都會選擇用虛擬私人網絡（VPN）「翻牆」，而近日廣東一名網民因此被當地警方處罰。<br />\n<br />\n網傳韶關市公安局對一名朱姓網民發出的通知，指其「擅自建立、使用非法定信道進行國際聯網」，違反內地互聯網的管理暫行規定，向他作出警告之餘，還罰款1000元人民幣（約1160港元）。朱表示，曾在手機安裝一個名為「藍燈」的「翻牆」軟件，其後連接自己家中的寬頻，瀏覽境外網站，懷疑因為在一星期內「翻牆」高達487次，過於頻繁因而被發現。<br />\n<br />\n另有傳重慶一名黃姓網民，亦因同樣原因於周五（4日）接獲榮昌區公安局發出通知書，傳喚他到公安局接受調查。"},{"pid":"e213a7b29a204382d4b47cbc5aadfd259a2365a8","tid":969665,"uid":143582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:40:26.000Z","msg":"翻牆都有曬紀錄，唔好以為無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36914c7846ddfe65b13f5f359a601e9b6669cd6","tid":969665,"uid":156363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e213a7b29a204382d4b47cbc5aadfd259a2365a8","tid":969665,"uid":143582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:40:26.000Z","msg":"翻牆都有曬紀錄，唔好以為無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:42:37.000Z","msg":"上過咩網，打過咩字都知道晒。"},{"pid":"a82d387ee254d188447d192480fbb7d90333d5e7","tid":969665,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T08:50:59.000Z","msg":"啲5毛見晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\